Our Approach 

Investor Education DayManaging Your Investments Planning Your Finances Preparing Your Estate PlanSelling Your Business Giving To Charity 









Altavista is an investment advisor and trust company serving individuals, families and institutions focused on the creation and preservation of wealth. The Altavista team is the realization that an investment firm can be approachable and personal without being limited in the investment choices offered to its clients.

We consider your priorities, long-term goals and the many aspects unique to your life in our comprehensive approach to managing your wealth. Our offices are located in Asheville, North Carolina and Charlotte, North Carolina.










 





	 

    






