Our Services 

Portfolio Management Asset Deployment and Allocation Trust Administration and Fiduciary Services Financial PlanningFamily Office Services Third-party Services for Legal and Accounting Practices Women in Conversation








			Financial Planning		

At Altavista financial planning is integrated with our investment management and fiduciary services as part of an ongoing process.  Financial Planning services include:

	 


Determining goals and objectives

A synopsis of the client’s estate plan, along with our recommended changes

Retirement planning

Formulation of an investment policy with asset allocation guidelines and suggested strategies

Cash flow planning and debt management strategies

Diversification and hedging strategies for those investors with large concentrations of wealth in a single stock or business

Analysis and coordination of employee benefits

Coordination of advice with the client’s legal, tax and other advisors

Tracking progress toward financial goals










 





	 

    






