	Mari Panzenhagen,

	Client Services Manager

Mari Panzenhagen joined our Asheville office as a client services manager for Altavista. She works directly with clients, custodial service teams, firm personnel and other advisors coordinating the management of client relationships and service requests. She facilitates trust administration for the Asheville office.

	 

She joined our client services team with 22 years experience in banking and personal trust services.  Mari is originally from Wisconsin. After 8 years of loan operations and personal banker service with SunTrust Bank in West Palm Beach, Mari and her family moved to the Mars Hill area.  In 1998, she continued her career as a Private Bank Trust Associate with Wachovia/Wells Fargo working in the administration of trust & investment management relationships.

	 

Mari enjoys cooking, reading and is a dedicated runner. She also enjoys family time with her husband Bill and son Matt.

	“By design, Altavista is focused exclusively on assisting you with the complex task of managing your wealth.”

	 

